    • getCapsulesInfo

      public String getCapsulesInfo()
      Returns information about the capsules in the current phase of the project. This method concatenates the details of the first valid capsule in the phase, along with its hashtags, into a single string and returns it.
      Returns:
      A string containing the details of the first valid capsule in the current phase of the project and its hashtags, separated by a newline character.

    • isThereRoomForAnotherCapsule

      public boolean isThereRoomForAnotherCapsule()
      Checks if there is room for another capsule in the current phase.
      Returns:
      true if there is room for another capsule, false otherwise.

    • getFirtsValidCapsule

      public int getFirtsValidCapsule()
      Returns the index of the first valid position to add a capsule capsule. If there is not space for more capsules it will return the lenght of the capsules's array times -1.
      Returns:
      The index of the first valid capsule.
